	<Title>
		Time your lotions right
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Apply moisturizers immediately after bathing. After washing or bathing, gently pat or blot your skin dry with a towel so that some moisture remains on the skin. Immediately moisturize your skin with an oil or cream to help trap water in the surface cells.&lt;/p&gt;
